name: You will find me at the corner.
description:
Not Surrounded By Decoration,
But there is a growing feeling,
not sad,
But colorful-- "

-there are times we choose to ignore the simplicity, but most of the time mystery found in ordinary things, in common  time, in usual circumstances ”.

("Hindi pinalilibitan Ng palamuti,
Pero may damdaming sumisidhi,
hindi malumbay,
Kundi makulay--"

-may mga pagkakataong pinipili nating hindi pansinin ang simple, pero palagi't laging matatagpuan ang hiwaga sa karaniwan, karaniwang panahon, karaniwang pagkakataon.")
